## 2. Architecture Overview

```
Chucks-list-MASTER.ods
        │
        ├── Export → Bulletins.csv ──► preprocess_bulletin_text.py
        │                                        │
        │                                        ▼
        │                              bulletins_data.csv
        │                                        │
        │                                        ▼
        │                             compile_bulletin.py
        │                                        │
        │                                        ▼
        │                    chucks_bulletin_final_output.html
        │                                        │
        │                                        ▼
        │                               ChucksBulletin/  ──► Zoho Campaigns
        │
        └── Export → Events.csv ──► preprocess_events_text.py
                                              │
                                              ▼
                                       events_data.csv
                                              │
                                              ▼
                                    compile_events.py
                                              │
                                              ▼
                          chucks_events_final_output.html
                                              │
                                              ▼
                                     ChucksEvents/  ──► Zoho Campaigns
```

Every stage is a separate Python subprocess. The entrypoint
(`Chucks_List_Builder.py`) orchestrates them in order and surfaces failures
immediately. It never collapses or merges the two pipelines.

